---
description: Next.js 14 + TypeScript + Tailwind + shadcn/ui conventions
globs: ["**/*.ts", "**/*.tsx"]
alwaysApply: false
---

- TypeScript strict mode. No any; use precise types or unknown + narrowing.
- Next.js 14 App Router only. Server Components by default; add use client only when a component needs state, effects, or browser APIs. Never use getServerSideProps / getStaticProps.
- Initial data fetching in server components or route handlers, not useEffect.
- UI from shadcn/ui + Tailwind utility classes. Recharts for the risk chart.
- Every async UI action handles loading and error states explicitly.
